GRAVINET WINTUN PLACEHOLDER (amd64)
This is a build-time placeholder, NOT the real Wintun driver, so the tree
compiles without shipping a binary blob. Replace it with the signed
wintun.dll for this architecture from https://www.wintun.net/
(wintun/bin/amd64/wintun.dll) to produce a self-contained Windows binary.
With this placeholder, the build still works and loads wintun.dll from
beside the .exe (or PATH) at runtime instead.
